Automation Quick Guide for the OmniStudio Build Tool

Understand how the Build Tool works with Salesforce DX, Jenkins, and compiling Lightning Web Components, OmniScripts, and FlexCards.

Build Tool with Salesforce DX
You can run Salesforce CLI commands in Jenkins.
Automatically Compile Lightning Web Component OmniScript and FlexCards 
The OmniStudio Build Tool can automatically compile and deploy Lightning Web Component (LWC) OmniScript and FlexCards after activation through Puppeteer or Chrome installed on your local machine.
